1074
00:56:17,336 --> 00:56:18,879
Okay. A hundred years
off my sentence

1075
00:56:18,962 --> 00:56:20,282
and a single cell
with no goblins.

1076
00:56:20,464 --> 00:56:21,965
Single cell and 55 years.

1077
00:56:22,132 --> 00:56:23,133
- Seventy-five.
- Sixty.

1078
00:56:23,300 --> 00:56:25,052
