- Done. Officers!

1079
00:56:25,469 --> 00:56:27,638
You reading me, Mulch?

1080
00:56:27,804 --> 00:56:29,806
Loud and clear, horsey.

1081
00:56:31,016 --> 00:56:33,769
Dwarfus Giaganticus.

1082
00:56:35,103 --> 00:56:37,439
Dwarfus Giaganticus.

1083
00:56:40,192 --> 00:56:41,193
Everybody,

1084
00:56:41,485 --> 00:56:42,903
stand back.

